        "id": 1017720
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-06-09T10:35:13Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I guess that `isValid` is, in a way, the \"isFoo\" version of `validates`. through that lens, I guess it\u0027s okay. but we need to very clearly document it.",
      "parentUuid": "f70c7fff_cbe773e8",
      "revId": "7a20952ac04e48723f9ec03769eee632cc3f5be4",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
